ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisOrder fixing the remuneration of PAUL ATERMAN, full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board and Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration Appeal Division (Head Office), for the period he is acting as Chairperson of the Immigration and Refugee Board, effective January 9, 2018, until such time as a new Chairperson is designated.
